{
  "message": "feat(skills): add creating-share-images skill for Next.js OG images\n\nAdd a comprehensive skill for generating OpenGraph and Twitter share\nimages in Next.js applications using next/og ImageResponse.\n\nThe skill includes:\n- SKILL.md with quick start template, design patterns, critical rules\n  for Satori rendering, color palettes by section type, and common\n  issues troubleshooting\n- references/patterns.md with extended visual patterns including\n  flywheel diagrams, document/writing visuals, code windows, network\n  hexagons, and journey path visualizations\n\nKey patterns covered:\n- Gradient backgrounds with glowing orbs for depth\n- Gradient text using backgroundClip: \"text\"\n- SVG icons with linearGradient fills\n- Proper dimensions (1200x630 OG, 1200x600 Twitter)\n- Two-column layouts with visual + text content\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
